@startuml Create Savings Plan Sequence

actor Parent
participant UI
participant API
participant PlanService
participant EventBus

Parent -> UI: Create new 529 plan
UI -> UI: Display plan wizard
Parent -> UI: Select plan type & beneficiary
Parent -> UI: Enter plan details
UI -> API: POST /api/savings-plans
API -> PlanService: CreateSavingsPlan(command)
PlanService -> PlanService: Validate plan details
PlanService -> EventBus: Raise SavingsPlanCreated
PlanService -> EventBus: Raise BeneficiaryAdded
PlanService --> API: PlanId
API --> UI: 201 Created
UI --> Parent: Success + setup contributions

@enduml
